{
  "id": "1TH.4",
  "bibleId": "de4e12af7f28f599-01",
  "number": "4",
  "bookId": "1TH",
  "reference": "1 Thessalonians 4",
  "copyright": "PUBLIC DOMAIN except in the United Kingdom, where a Crown Copyright applies to printing the KJV. See http://www.cambridge.org/about-us/who-we-are/queens-printers-patent",
  "verseCount": 18,
  "content": [
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "1",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "1",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Furthermore then we beseech you, brethren, and exhort ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "you",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.1",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.1"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " by the Lord Jesus, that as ye have received of us how ye ought to walk and to please God, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "so",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.1",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.1"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ye would abound more and more. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "2",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:2"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "2",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For ye know what commandments we gave you by the Lord Jesus. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.2",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.2"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "3",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:3"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "3",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For this is the will of God, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "even",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.3",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.3"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " your sanctification, that ye should abstain from fornication: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "4",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:4"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "4",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "That every one of you should know how to possess his vessel in sanctification and honour; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "5",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:5"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "5",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Not in the lust of concupiscence, even as the Gentiles which know not God: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.5",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.5"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "6",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:6"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "6",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "That no ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "man",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.6",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.6"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " go beyond and defraud his brother in ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "any",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.6",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.6"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " matter: because that the Lord ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "is",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.6",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.6"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " the avenger of all such, as we also have forewarned you and testified. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "7",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:7"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "7",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For God hath not called us unto uncleanness, but unto holiness. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "8",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:8"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "8",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "He therefore that despiseth, despiseth not man, but God, who hath also given unto us his holy Spirit. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.8",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.8"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "9",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:9"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "9",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "But as touching brotherly love ye need not that I write unto you: for ye yourselves are taught of God to love one another. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "10",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:10"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "10",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And indeed ye do it toward all the brethren which are in all Macedonia: but we beseech you, brethren, that ye increase more and more; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "11",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:11"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "11",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And that ye study to be quiet, and to do your own business, and to work with your own hands, as we commanded you; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.11",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "12",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:12"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "12",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "That ye may walk honestly toward them that are without, and ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.12",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.12"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "that",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.12",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.12"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ye may have lack of nothing.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.12",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.12"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "13",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:13"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "13",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "But I would not have you to be ignorant, brethren, concerning them which are asleep, that ye sorrow not, even as others which have no hope. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.13",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.13"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "14",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:14"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "14",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For if we believe that Jesus died and rose again, even so them also which sleep in Jesus will God bring with him. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.14",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.14"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "15",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:15"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "15",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For this we say unto you by the word of the Lord, that we which are alive ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.15",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.15"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "and",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.15",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.15"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " remain unto the coming of the Lord shall not prevent them which are asleep. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.15",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.15"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "16",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:16"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "16",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For the Lord himself shall descend from heaven with a shout, with the voice of the archangel, and with the trump of God: and the dead in Christ shall rise first: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.16",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "17",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:17"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "17",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Then we which are alive ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.17",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "and",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.4.17",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.4.17"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " remain shall be caught up together with them in the clouds, to meet the Lord in the air: and so shall we ever be with the Lord. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.17",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "18",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 4:18"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "18",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Wherefore comfort one another with these words.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.4.18",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.4.18"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
